kmod-profiler (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
    - Per-kernel observation and snapshot tracking
    - Grace-period handling for modules new to a kernel update
    - systemd timer for periodic sampling
    - Path watcher for DKMS / out-of-tree driver changes
    - Kernel package hooks for Debian (postinst.d) and systemd
      kernel-install (install.d)
    - Mitigates Dirty Frag (esp4/esp6/rxrpc) on systems that don't
      legitimately use IPsec or AFS.

 -- kmod-profiler maintainers <root@localhost>  Thu, 07 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
